### ü•à **2. Google Developers / Chrome DevTools**

* **Website:** [https://developer.chrome.com/](https://developer.chrome.com/)
* **Why it‚Äôs great:** Official guidance on web standards, performance, accessibility, and tools like Lighthouse & DevTools.
* **Topics Covered:**

  * Core Web Vitals
  * Web performance
