### ‚úÖ **4. W3C & Web.dev (by Google)**

* **W3C (Web Standards):** [https://www.w3.org/](https://www.w3.org/)
* **Web.dev:** [https://web.dev/learn/](https://web.dev/learn/)
* **Why it‚Äôs great:** Both are about best practices and keeping up with the evolution of web standards.

